agon-and-the-oracle</link><description>威胁是针对图书馆员的。威胁在于仍然进入六边形的少数、正在消失的人口。谁还从书架上抽出一本书。谁还花三天时间读它。谁仍然关闭它并感觉发生了变化。这种做法不是一种爱好。这是一项技术。一种比印刷本更古老，比手抄本更古老，甚至可能比文字更古老。这是一个在人类头骨内组装的过程。那种耐心、连续、集中和具体的注意力会产生我们过去所说的理解。人工智能不会产生这种关注。人工智能产生一种与注意力非常相似的感觉，但又是另一种东西，就像糖精产生一种与甜味非常相似的感觉，但又是另一种东西。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/the-hexagon-and-the-oracle.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 01:13:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/the-hexagon-and-the-oracle</guid></item><item><title>Iain McGilchrist——人工智能能变得有意识吗？</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/iain-mcgilchrist-can-ai-become-conscious</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 00:58:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/iain-mcgilchrist-can-ai-become-conscious</guid></item><item><title>泛灵论的新对手——山姆·科尔曼</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/a-new-rival-to-panpsychism-sam-coleman</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 00:43:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/a-new-rival-to-panpsychism-sam-coleman</guid></item><item><title>人类思维可以被人为扩展，人工智能也可以</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/human-minds-could-be-artificially-expanded-and-so-can-ai</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 00:28:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/human-minds-could-be-artificially-expanded-and-so-can-ai</guid></item><item><title>牛津物理学家说，你在其他宇宙中的版本可能会微妙地影响你的命运</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/versions-of-you-in-other-universes-may-be-subtly-affecting-your-destiny-oxford-physicist-says</link><description>您可能认为您是自己故事的主角。然而，根据牛津物理学家 Vlatko Vedral 的说法，你更像是一个木偶——它的线在任何给定时间都被拉入一百万个平行宇宙。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/versions-of-you-in-other-universes-may-be-subtly-affecting-your-destiny-oxford-physicist-says.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 00:13:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/versions-of-you-in-other-universes-may-be-subtly-affecting-your-destiny-oxford-physicist-says</guid></item><item><title>研究发现，一个比饮食或运动更能预测长寿的关键因素</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/one-critical-factor-predicts-longevity-better-than-diet-or-exercise-study-finds</link><description>研究表明，饮食和锻炼都是影响寿命的因素，但它们并不是寿命的唯一最大预测因素。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/one-critical-factor-predicts-longevity-better-than-diet-or-exercise-study-finds2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 23:58:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/one-critical-factor-predicts-longevity-better-than-diet-or-exercise-study-finds</guid></item><item><title>您只需要数学 2 — 变压器残余流中的符号稳定行为纤维</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/mathematics-is-all-you-need-2-sign-stabilized-behavioral-fibers-in-transformer-residual-streams</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 23:43:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/mathematics-is-all-you-need-2-sign-stabilized-behavioral-fibers-in-transformer-residual-streams</guid></item></channel></rss>